metadata.name: Buffalo Chicken Wing Asteroid
metadata.description:
Drifting in space waiting to be mined, Shaped like a 
Buffalo chicken wing, this asteroid contains more than 90 tons of platinum worth up to 10 trillion US dollars. 

This is the first piece from my upcoming short film "VITA".

Artwork Information:

Software used: Adobe After Effects, Autodesk Maya
Dimensions: 2664 x 2398 px
File format: Mp4, H.264, 30 fps
